        <mxCell id="hivemq" value="HiveMQ Cloud&lt;br&gt;Broker MQTT&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Host cloud&lt;br&gt;Puerto 8883 TLS&lt;br&gt;Usuarios separados para ESP, bridge y API&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Topic base:&lt;br&gt;monitor-servidores/rack01/#" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e5dbff;strokeColor=#7048e8;fontSize=14;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="layer_network">
